5年以下有期徒刑。\r\n施用第二級毒品者，處3年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c349%2c20220310%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,349,20220310,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"349","JDATE":"20220310","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}